----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Size of data types and their pointers for 64 bits architecture
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Size of char: 1 ----- size of char pointer: 8
Size of int: 4 ----- size of int pointer: 8
Size of float: 4 ----- size of float pointer: 8
Size of double: 8 ----- size of double pointer: 8
Size of long double: 16 ----- size of long double pointer: 8
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
-    Conclusion: size of pointer is always 8 bytes for 64 bits device      -
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

